text: Rhys Wakefield (born 20 November 1988) is an Australian actor. He started his career in 2000. He is best known for his roles in the movies The Black Balloon (2008), Sanctum (2011) and The Purge (2013). He also appeared as Lucas Holden in the soap opera Home and Away from 2005 to 2008. Wakefield was born in Cairns, Queensland.
